index-banner-description: Make your desk beautiful and organized. Post a picture to social media and watch it get more likes than life-changing announcements. Reflect on the shallow nature of existence. At least you have a really nice desk setup.
index-collection-description: Each season, we collaborate with world-class designers to create a collection inspired by the natural world.
index-last-description: Endless tasks, limited hours, a single piece of paper. Not really a haiku, but we're doing our best here. No kanban boards, burndown charts, or tangled flowcharts with our Focus system. Just the undeniable urge to fill empty circles.
